{{Infobox ethnic group |group = Afro-Jordanians |image = |pop = '''~60,000'''<ref>http://www.africanviews.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=105 Jordan</ref> |langs = [[Arabic language|Arabic]] |rels = [[Islam]] |related-c = }}
'''Afro-Jordanians''' or '''African-Jordanians''', are an ethnic group that is descended from people of [[Black people|Black African]] heritage in [[Jordan]]. Most Afro-Jordanians speak [[Arabic language|Arabic]] and adhere to [[Islam]].
