'''Aja''' are an ethnic group in the [[South Sudan]] state of [[Western Bahr el Ghazal]].  They mostly live along the upper reaches of the [[Sopo River]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gurtong.org/resourcecenter/people/profile_tribe.asp?TribeID=131 |title=Gurtong Peace Project |access-date=2009-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090218020803/http://www.gurtong.org/resourcecenter/people/profile_tribe.asp?TribeID=131 |archive-date=2009-02-18 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref>

