'''Vizzuality''' is a [[science]] and [[technology]] company focused on data visualization, web-GIS and tool development and committed to working on projects related to [[conservation (ethic)|conservation]], the [[environment (biophysical)|environment]] and [[sustainable development]]. They have two offices, in [[Madrid]] and [[Cambridge]].{{cn|date=October 2015}}
Vizzuality is a member of the board of directors of [[Citizen Science Alliance]] that owned and operated the [[citizen science]] web portal [[Zooniverse (citizen science project)|Zooniverse]].<ref name=ESERO>{{cite web| title=New Zooniverse projects – Bat Detective and Click to Cure| url=http://www.esero.org.uk/news/new-zooniverse-projects-bat-detective-and-click-to-cure| publisher=European Space Education Resource Office| date=30 October 2012| accessdate=8 October 2014| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014070524/http://www.esero.org.uk/news/new-zooniverse-projects-bat-detective-and-click-to-cure| archive-date=14 October 2014| dead-url=yes| df=dmy-all}}</ref>
